features: THE EXTREME ODOR ELIMINATOR: Don't mask nasty odors with flowery air fresheners, eliminate them with FunkAway Odor Eliminating Beads. These odor absorbing beads soak up funky smells and remove them from the air.

WORKS ON ALL SMELLS: FunkAway's supercharged beads work on pet, smoke, bathroom, mildew, gym, closet, kitchen and gamer stink. Place the jar of absorber beads in any place that smells and enjoy refreshed air.

LONG-LASTING RESULTS: Live funk free for up to 90 days! FunkAway's deodorizer beads work hard to keep your space smelling clean by breaking down and eliminating offensive odors for long-lasting freshness.

POWERFUL FORMULA: Unlike conventional room fresheners, FunkAway's supercharged beads eliminate the toughest airborne odors. Keep any room smelling fresh with the exclusive OM Complex. It’s guaranteed to work.
LIVE A FUNK-FREE LIFE: Shop our full catalog of odor elimination products to control everything from car odors to sweat smells and even cannabis stench – all made in the USA.
body.description: FunkAway 12-ounce Odor Eliminating Beads are supercharged with our exclusive OM Complex that doesn't just cover up odors, it eliminates them! Place a jar in your locker, closet, basement, bathroom or anywhere funky odors are a problem. LIVE FUNK FREE for up to 90 days – satisfaction guaranteed! The odor eliminator beads are perfect for homeowners, gym rats, athletes, pet owners or anyone else with stinky spaces. We tried the other odor eliminators, but they just covered up the odors. We needed something that eliminated the grossest, most extreme, sickest smells you've ever smelled. The kind you find in hockey locker rooms, garbage dumps, public restrooms, or even worse, a teenager's bedroom. We locked ourselves in a lab and didn't leave until we had the solution – our exclusive OM Complex! Now we have a whole line of extreme odor eliminators, and we're always working on something new.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 23, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Works so well!!
reviews.reviewText: Honestly, I didn't really have high expectations for it to work so well because it seemed like a cheaper alternative to other brands. But wow am I glad I was wrong! I have a small dog who's potty trained to pee in those pee pads so obviously there will be urine odors in between changes. I find with traditional room spray it just masks and blends with the smell. Anyways, I opened it and left in a high shelf at the source of the smell and not even kidding.. within 25-30 minutes the smell is GONE. Whenever I do smell a little linger of odor, I shake the container a bit and POOF! Works miraculously well. 10/10.I will write back when I do have to make another purchase to see how long they last. The label says good up to 90 days but I'm sure it will be less than that..

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Ordered by mistake - not sure about this
reviews.reviewText: We had a funky smell in our bathroom sinks. I was looking on Amazon for something that I could put down the drain and get rid of the smell. I saw this product in the category that I searched but when I got the product found out this is more of an air freshener with a bunches Plastic bubble pieces in a jar that you shake up and then the smell comes out? We still smell the smell in the sink and found out it’s best to use white vinegar and baking soda to get rid of that. When you shake these jars, it does smell nice for about five minutes and then you don’t smell it anymore. I’m not sure if it’s just an air freshener but it does not clean anything in your sink if that’s what you’re looking for. it does have a nice smell. It just doesn’t do the job that I was looking for.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 12, 2022
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Good product, BAD container
reviews.reviewText: I love the way this makes my work truck smell clean and not like a work truck. The beads are cool to have and look at.….but there’s a problem. The container SUUUCKS. It needs a better way of sealing it. The top falls off way too easy. I hit a bump on the road, the jar rolled and hit the ground and there were beads everywhere…. It was frustrating because besides some dirt I keep a neat truck.I’ve bought 3 of these and 2 of them the lid popped off and beads everywhere and the third was stolen when the truck was in the shop.This product needs a threaded lid upgrade and needs to be able to fit in a cup holder to make this product more vehicle friendly.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 1.0 out of 5 stars Don’t waste your money
reviews.reviewText: I bought this to put on the lid of my cat’s litter box- because let’s face it, even when you clean the litter box every day, it still smells unpleasant- but I am very disappointed in this product.It smells decent, but it doesn’t absorb odor as advertised, nor does it emit enough fragrance to mask odor.Don’t waste your money. You’re better off buying one of those automatic air fresheners.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 9, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This stuff really works!!!
reviews.reviewText: Our dog is kept in our home office for several hours a day while we are away. Naturally, she has biological needs during the day which she takes care of on the pee pads. We purchased the Funkaway Bead product and NO MORE ODOR!!! Only took a few hours for the odor to be eliminated and the room stays fresh smelling all day-THANK YOU!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Just get it
reviews.reviewText: I wont lie, I had my reservations about this product. It reminds me of those little scent things that you put in your car under the seat to help with smell and you just kinda hope for the best. However, this thing is powerful. I just recently adopted a new cat. He's about 8 months old now. His poops....good lord. Are terrible. I put this thing on my desk in my room, NO WHERE NEAR THE LITTER BOX and came home to my room smelling amazing. It's been weeks now and it's still going strong. I have ordered another one for my living room because I'm tired of being those little air wick things. You will NOT be disappointed in this!

We have a family cottage that is closed for the winter and gets a very stale smell. These beads took about a day to clear each room-I kept it moving from room to room and then I bought 2
Well, we really liked this product. Then it QUADRUPLED in price. What the heck? $60+ for a room deodoriser. I guess for Americans only now, definitely not for us.

I was skeptical based on the other bad reviews but I'm glad that I tried it for myself. I put the beads in my walk in closet at the bottom with all of my shoes and after one week the stale smell was completely gone! I haven't even had a whiff of stink since! I would absolutely recommend this product and would purchase again.

Doesn't work at all. We put this in the shoe basket hoping to relieve some of the funkiness of the shoe odors and it doesn't work at all. It has has a fresh scent to it, but I feel like it's just working to mask odors not draw them from the air specifically.
